      "message": "I am not sure for how long the Access service will live. It was designed before Realms, and Realm libs supported all of its usage, so there was a medium term to remove it, perhaps as a part of Go rewrite.\n\nHowever, needing the access info in the browser was not anticipated. We don\u0027t have the replicated Realms db here.\n+Vadim WDYT?\nShould we maybe expose some central API in CIA, now that CIA is aware of all realms and permissions?",
